17-06-17T05:26:26.000Z","msg":"記得backup"},{"pid":"61315b8dcaf82a9a869500756111912b9b7a3540","tid":285953,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T05:27:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ac4d27276dc7848ce639e2f63f677215c4536ac","tid":285953,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T05:27:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>保安局好快會收到律師信</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲報左警<br />\n<br />\n黑警一陣會唔會走去爆禁毒處拉人?"},{"pid":"48b9ce35705880b6d7b07cc41653576e5601716e","tid":285953,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T05:28:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>於一九七七年，當局也下令通緝馬惜如<br />\n和馬惜珍兩兄弟（他們是吳錫豪以前的同黨），<br />\n打算控以在一九六八至七四年期間偷運700<span style=\"color: red;\">噸</span>鴉片<br />\n入口。馬惜如在警方執行逮捕令前潛逃至台灣<br />\n（當時台灣與香港並無引渡安排），其弟馬惜珍<br />\n則在一九七七年八月被檢控，但在保釋期間同樣逃往台灣。馬惜如於一九九八年在台灣逝世，但其弟至今仍在警方通緝名單上。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1d15590fc15c83745939e3d4415c21e2b62a0c89","tid":285953,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T05:32:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖然係保安局出，但係一樣係告連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係政府文件"},{"pid":"89428bcb266af92fb8db24668ed13a120cfbbb62","tid":285953,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T05:45:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>雖然係保安局出，但係一樣係告連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係政府文件</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a82fc3c106951b5ad793de346a84c68e789d6edd","tid":285953,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T05:46:08.000Z","msg":"實捉到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"513d6ad04282814fcaa798a0ae18b9c36eb0d643","tid":285953,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T05:53:46.000Z","msg":"人地嬲妳話人地賣粉 其係人地賣片"},{"pid":"b9dc3efe8cad8be72d133acb8bf8a6c42876f385","tid":285953,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T06:16:41.000Z","msg":"35.  Ms Cheong for the defendants relied heavily in the decision of Recorder J. Leong, SC in Poon Ying Hon v. CCT Telecom Holdings Ltd &amp; Anor, HCA3431/2001 (unreported, 17 August 2001) at &sect;&sect;27-29 and 40 :<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;[27] The nature of the jurisdiction is defined in Gatley on Libel and Slander, 9th Edition at paragraph 25.2 as follows :<br />\n<br />\nThe jurisdiction to grant interlocutory injunctions to restrain publication of defamatory statements is &lsquo;of a delicate nature&rsquo;, which &lsquo;ought only to be exercised in the clearest cases&rsquo;.  That was stated by Lord Esher M.R. in Coulson v. Coulson and it encapsulates the general approach of the Court.  The reluctance to grant peremptory injunctions is rooted in the importance attached to the right of free speech.  Thus the Court will only grant an interlocutory injunction where,<br />\n<br />\n(1)   the statement is unarguably defamatory;<br />\n<br />\n(2)   there are no grounds for concluding the statement may be true;<br />\n<br />\n(3)   there is no other defence which might succeed;<br />\n<br />\n(4)   there is evidence of an intention to repeat or publish the defamatory statement.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 政府緝毒史實都唔係true?"},{"pid":"6e6906409c4beddcc1089953471e766c4dea0945","tid":285953,"uid":80944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T06:17:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41bd982ccf180057cc83c11785e8f6c5f36fbc1b","tid":285953,"uid":59922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T06:21:36.000Z","msg":"g持告9禁毒處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f86a073c06262c993bd0cacaafcad88078788ed","tid":285953,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T06:23:36.000Z","msg":"(2)     In respect of the 1st , 2nd &amp; 3rd offending words and the 64 statements, it can be said that the defendants have good arguable defence in that :<br />\n<br />\n          (a)    there was no publication by the defendants;<br />\n<br />\n          (b)    the defendants may only be innocent disseminators; and<br />\n<br />\n          (c)    some of the words complained of either contain no clear references to the plaintiffs, or are otherwise not defamatory.<br />\n<br />\n同埋當年high court first instance判果陣, 都唔係話1st-3rd 所有言論都屬於誹謗"},{"pid":"59dabbb2163d7156321c1141c736f2788dfc47dd","tid":285953,"uid":7840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T06:33:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"998c2073deb567639832205ebd8078c951b1ac79","tid":285953,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T06:36:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾時告香港政府誹謗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上次判呢單野係告唔入架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c4c1dd21c9000464d40f169ae6981ae8d2dd391","tid":285953,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T06:43:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幾時告香港政府誹謗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上次判呢單野係告唔入架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上次東方報業集團無告果幾個nickname上庭"},{"pid":"40bfad5734be8ea4c413b8664281bc19f332e2d1","tid":285953,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T06:46:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c8d21ca055ad8b4bec224c26570bd5d0f141f52","tid":285953,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T06:46:59.000Z","msg":"發揮第四權<br />\n雖難必誅<br />\n實捉到你"},{"pid":"a15c1b50c0cf17a852804148a1c0a4627c3b066d","tid":285953,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T06:48:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幾時告香港政府誹謗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上次判呢單野係告唔入架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上次東方報業集團無告果幾個nickname上庭</blockquote><br />\n不過都好睇果幾個nickname嗡過啲乜<br />\n<br />\n湯川學嗡就關於馬惜珍最多, 不過佢講埋馬惜珍屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上訴庭:<br />\n<br />\n In respect of the Jan 2009 words, the Judge found that they were defamatory of the plaintiffs in the second action in that theyimputed that the two newspapers, the Oriental Daily News and The Sun, were founded with drug money, that they were involved in drugtrafficking and/or money-laundering activities and/or immoral activities and that they were corrupt, illegal, immoral and unethical. He found that those words also imputed that Mr Ma was a member of a family involved in drug trafficking and/or was a member of orassociated with the 14K triad society."},{"pid":"1695ba2e5c09e9f02df299c4cd9563e05d5eb518","tid":285953,"uid":47298,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T06:48:56.000Z","msg":"被捕就事實<br />\n佢地應該冇判到走左佬？<br />\n所以你話佢地咩咩就可能係誹謗<br />\n利申：9up"},{"pid":"474fb41c9da235e33226a5ac63473450e85b5f7a","tid":285953,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T06:54:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>被捕就事實<br />\n佢地應該冇判到走左佬？<br />\n所以你話佢地咩咩就可能係誹謗<br />\n利申：9up</blockquote><br />\n人都死左, 點告<br />\n假設佢人仲在生, 馬惜珍先係一個通緝犯, 佢甩到條妨礙司法公正/「棄保潛逃」罪先算<br />\n再黎再要甩毒販個名, 陳慶偉法官都話就算doj唔夠料入佢, 都唔代表佢係無辜<br />\n之後馬惜珍先可以用1st plaintiff 身份去告人誹謗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nwhich is impossible"},{"pid":"4996f13ee8211a08e0f7e4530446fedb54cd540f","tid":285953,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T07:02:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>被捕就事實<br />\n佢地應該冇判到走左佬？<br />\n所以你話佢地咩咩就可能係誹謗<br />\n利申：9up</blockquote><br />\n人都死左, 點告<br />\n假設佢人仲在生, 馬惜珍先係一個通緝犯, 佢甩到條妨礙司法公正/「棄保潛逃」罪先算<br />\n再黎再要甩毒販個名, 陳慶偉法官都話就算doj唔夠料入佢, 都唔代表佢係無辜<br />\n之後馬惜珍先可以用1st plaintiff 身份去告人誹謗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nwhich is impossible</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n姐係如果講報紙個d巴打應該會出事??"},{"pid":"3fe4f14156fb8c8aa51d461ce4f3cf14d27b95eb","tid":285953,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T07:11:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>被捕就事實<br />\n佢地應該冇判到走左佬？<br />\n所以你話佢地咩咩就可能係誹謗<br />\n利申：9up</blockquote><br />\n人都死左, 點告<br />\n假設佢人仲在生, 馬惜珍先係一個通緝犯, 佢甩到條妨礙司法公正/「棄保潛逃」罪先算<br />\n再黎再要甩毒販個名, 陳慶偉法官都話就算doj唔夠料入佢, 都唔代表佢係無辜<br />\n之後馬惜珍先可以用1st plaintiff 身份去告人誹謗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nwhich is impossible</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n姐係如果講報紙個d巴打應該會出事??</blockquote><br />\n6.  The tort of libel has as its aim the protection of a person&rsquo;s reputation.  A person&rsquo;s reputation consists of what others think of him or her.   That reputation is damaged when a defendant publishes or communicates to a third person a defamatory statement (that is, a statement tending to lower someone in the estimation of right-thinking members of society generally[10]) about the person defamed.  It follows that the act of publication is a fundamental constituent of the tort. <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先要成為一個person, 你先會俾人告, 死人係法律上都無行為能力<br />\n再黎講prove<br />\n<br />\n馬惜珍而家連入場資格都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nHCA2140/2008單野係講到報業集團先出事(which is not my intention)"},{"pid":"1b4ccfcb4a8224a5e63d6a0b2a7ba78c11689071","tid":285953,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T07:51:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c11889b344e15c358c10bbe9477162466368230f","tid":285953,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T02:04:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1ba5f3c3ad54c0f7186d16ee00d895f56d8420bf","tid":285953,"uid":71231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T05:15:06.000Z","msg":"推下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"870ac570c8754c6b7dcaceeac4e5af19fdd3e8a2","tid":285953,"uid":71231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T07:10:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe231d8c511aea07981bfe2af23005f7ecf147e","tid":285953,"uid":85131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T13:14:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c10fc83e6e5652033e071ab07a307310dd8b82","tid":285953,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T13:27:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>湯川學嗡就關於馬惜珍最多, 不過佢講埋馬惜珍屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n湯川學就最後好似無被告上庭<br />\n連道歉都無, 似乎time barred埋<br />\n<br />\n點解呢?<br />\n<br />\n湯川學就住西營盤, 我唔知佢係咪寶翠園或半山嗰堆啦<br />\n若果佢有錢, 打算真打<br />\n去prove fair comment, 咁咪真係係open court研討馬惜珍既背景?<br />\n原告想唔想咁做先?<br />\n<br />\n一陣辯護方搵到個前三合會專家既退休黑警去做專家證人<br />\n咁原告個風險咪好大?"},{"pid":"04a5e96915ecd414a702f402e2dcc92492a5d464","tid":285953,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T13:29:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>湯川學嗡就關於馬惜珍最多, 不過佢講埋馬惜珍屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n湯川學就最後好似