\n<br />\n紅登個律師, miss左申請陪審團時限既court rules<br />\n<br />\n搞到上次誹謗case無出陪審團<br />\n<br />\n誹謗係少數可以用陪審團既case黎<br />\n<br />\n陪審團會決定, 究竟一句說話係咪誹謗<br />\n<br />\n若果下次出到jury, 班友死口裁定唔係誹謗<br />\n咁原告就好好笑啦"},{"pid":"45ca4993b3ef7b14180d7da83e6f2aaaa9a42db3","tid":285953,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T15:25:13.000Z","msg":"幾十年了 <br />\n真的假不了"},{"pid":"7ea108719015b3f002cd24c50cf14ed8704daf6d","tid":285953,"uid":5419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T15:29:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾十年了 <br />\n真的假不了</blockquote><br />\n有種就告政府囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44be83f370b704d036186be23771704905f64c2e","tid":285953,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T15:37:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幾十年了 <br />\n真的假不了</blockquote><br />\n有種就告政府囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n保安局驚到腳震未?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c9ba1b03d35f98b4b26d6c5c118e57179d40c54","tid":285953,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T15:51:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港政府係咪發放虛假消息？我聽到呢個消息覺得嚴重不安，希望東方可控告政府誹謗，釋除公罪疑慮，維護社會公義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英女皇迫害忠良"},{"pid":"29f153dd8b3688a5526e887d3582404ecff8b64c","tid":285953,"uid":71231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T23:01:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c6c02c060211449c9cecdfbed5f7285c04f82ce","tid":285953,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T01:44:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34da90f16db4c1c5e5fcfe2aba43a4ac5fa2c0f9","tid":285953,"uid":85131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20